     1→# API.md — LookUp API Reference
     2→
     3→> Read `docs/AGENT.md` first. This covers: (1) Internal Backend API, (2) Shopee External API integration, (3) TikTok External API integration.
     4→
     5→---
     6→
     7→## Internal Backend API
     8→
     9→**Base URL (dev):** `http://localhost:3000`
    10→**Base URL (prod):** `https://api.lookup.app`
    11→**Format:** All requests/responses in JSON. Multipart for image uploads.
    12→**Auth:** `Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>` on all `/api/*` routes except auth.
    13→
    14→### Standard Response Envelope
    15→
    16→```typescript
    17→// Success
    18→{
    19→  "success": true,
    20→  "data": { ... },
    21→  "meta": { "page": 1, "total": 100 }   // only on paginated responses
    22→}
    23→
    24→// Error
    25→{
    26→  "success": false,
    27→  "error": {
    28→    "code": "SHOP_NOT_FOUND",
    29→    "message": "Shop with id abc123 not found",
    30→    "details": {}   // optional, zod validation errors etc
    31→  }
    32→}
    33→```
    34→
    35→### Standard Error Codes
    36→
    37→| Code | HTTP | Meaning |
    38→|------|------|---------|
    39→| `UNAUTHORIZED` | 401 | Missing or invalid JWT |
    40→| `FORBIDDEN` | 403 | JWT valid but no permission |
    41→| `NOT_FOUND` | 404 | Resource not found |
    42→| `VALIDATION_ERROR` | 422 | Request body failed Zod validation |
    43→| `PLATFORM_ERROR` | 502 | Shopee/TikTok API returned error |
    44→| `RATE_LIMITED` | 429 | Too many requests |
    45→| `SHOP_NOT_CONNECTED` | 400 | Shop OAuth not completed |
    46→| `TOKEN_EXPIRED` | 401 | Shopee/TikTok access token expired |
    47→
