    50→## Module: Auth
    51→
    52→### POST /api/auth/register
    53→Register new user account.
    54→
    55→**Request Body:**
    56→```typescript
    57→{
    58→  email: string;       // valid email
    59→  password: string;    // min 8 chars
    60→  name: string;        // min 2 chars
    61→}
    62→```
    63→
    64→**Response 201:**
    65→```typescript
    66→{
    67→  success: true;
    68→  data: {
    69→    user: { id: string; email: string; name: string; };
    70→    accessToken: string;    // JWT, expires in 15m
    71→    refreshToken: string;   // opaque token, expires in 30d
    72→  }
    73→}
    74→```
