   130→## Module: Shops
   131→
   132→### GET /api/shops/shopee/auth-url
   133→Generate Shopee OAuth authorization URL for user to open in WebView.
   134→
   135→**Query Params:** none
   136→
   137→**Response 200:**
   138→```typescript
   139→{
   140→  success: true;
   141→  data: {
   142→    url: string;        // Shopee OAuth URL with HMAC signed params
   143→    state: string;      // CSRF state token (store this, verify in callback)
   144→  }
   145→}
   146→```
   147→
   148→---
   149→
   150→### GET /api/shops/shopee/callback
   151→Called by Shopee after user authorizes. Handle via deep link or server redirect.
   152→
   153→**Query Params:**
   154→```
   155→code: string        // authorization code from Shopee
   156→shop_id: string     // Shopee shop ID
   157→state: string       // must match state from auth-url
   158→```
   159→
   160→**Response 200:**
   161→```typescript
   162→{
   163→  success: true;
   164→  data: {
   165→    shop: {
   166→      id: string;             // internal shop ID
   167→      platformShopId: string; // Shopee's shop_id
   168→      shopName: string;
   169→      platform: "SHOPEE";
   170→      region: string;         // e.g. "ID", "MY"
   171→      connectedAt: string;
   172→    }
   173→  }
   174→}
   175→```
   176→
