   346→## Module: Inventory (Stock)
   347→
   348→### PATCH /api/inventory/:productId
   349→Update stock for one or more variants of a product.
   350→
   351→**Request Body:**
   352→```typescript
   353→{
   354→  shopId: string;
   355→  updates: Array<{
   356→    variantId: string;
   357→    stock: number;        // min: 0, max: 999999
   358→  }>;
   359→}
   360→```
   361→
   362→**Response 200:**
   363→```typescript
   364→{
   365→  success: true;
   366→  data: {
   367→    updated: Array<{
   368→      variantId: string;
   369→      previousStock: number;
   370→      newStock: number;
   371→    }>;
   372→    platform: "SHOPEE" | "TIKTOK";
   373→    updatedAt: string;
   374→  }
   375→}
   376→```
   377→
   378→**Possible errors:** `VALIDATION_ERROR`, `SHOP_NOT_CONNECTED`, `PLATFORM_ERROR`
