   577→## Module: Webhooks (Public, No Auth)
   578→
   579→### POST /webhooks/shopee
   580→Receive Shopee push notifications.
   581→
   582→**Headers:** `Authorization: <Shopee-generated signature>`
   583→
   584→**Body:** Shopee webhook payload (varies by event type)
   585→
   586→**Response:** Always `200 OK` immediately, process async.
   587→
   588→---
   589→
   590→### POST /webhooks/tiktok
   591→Receive TikTok Shop webhook events.
   592→
   593→**Headers:** Custom TikTok signature headers
   594→
   595→**Body:** TikTok event payload
   596→
   597→**Response:** Always `200 OK` immediately.
