   600→
   601→### GET /api/events/stream
   602→Server-Sent Events stream for real-time client updates.
   603→
   604→**Headers:** `Accept: text/event-stream`
   605→
   606→**Events pushed:**
   607→```
   608→event: inventory_updated
   609→data: { "productId": "...", "shopId": "...", "variantId": "...", "newStock": 5 }
   610→
   611→event: price_updated
   612→data: { "productId": "...", "shopId": "...", "newPrice": 50000 }
   613→
   614→event: bulk_progress
   615→data: { "jobId": "...", "progress": 45, "successCount": 90 }
