   620→## External: Shopee Open API v2
   621→
   622→**Base URL:** `https://partner.shopeemobile.com`
   623→**Auth:** HMAC-SHA256 signature on every request.
   624→
   625→**Signature formula:**
   626→```
   627→sign = HMAC_SHA256(
   628→  partner_key,
   629→  "{partner_id}{api_path}{timestamp}{access_token}{shop_id}"
   630→)
   631→```
   632→
   633→### Key Endpoints Used
   634→
   635→| Method | Path | Description |
   636→|--------|------|-------------|
   637→| GET | `/api/v2/shop/get_shop_info` | Get shop detail |
   638→| GET | `/api/v2/product/get_item_list` | List products |
   639→| GET | `/api/v2/product/get_item_base_info` | Product detail |
   640→| POST | `/api/v2/product/update_stock` | Update stock |
   641→| POST | `/api/v2/product/update_price_info` | Update price |
   642→| POST | `/api/v2/product/update_item` | Update product (images) |
   643→| POST | `/api/v2/media_space/upload_image` | Upload image |
   644→| GET | `/api/v2/auth/token/get` | Exchange code for token |
   645→| POST | `/api/v2/auth/access_token/get` | Refresh access token |
   646→
   647→**Rate Limit:** Varies by endpoint. Typically 10-100 calls/second. Implement 200ms delay between batch calls.
   648→
   649→**Shopee Update Stock Request:**
   650→```typescript
   651→POST /api/v2/product/update_stock
   652→{
   653→  item_id: number;
   654→  stock_list: Array<{
   655→    model_id: number;    // 0 if no variant
   656→    seller_stock: Array<{ stock: number }>;
   657→  }>;
   658→}
   659→```
   660→
   661→**Shopee Update Price Request:**
   662→```typescript
   663→POST /api/v2/product/update_price_info
   664→{
   665→  item_id: number;
   666→  price_list: Array<{
   667→    model_id: number;
   668→    original_price: number;
   669→    current_price?: number;
   670→  }>;
   671→}
   672→```
   673→
   674→---
   675→
   676→## External: TikTok Shop Open API
   677→
   678→**Base URL:** `https://open-api.tiktokglobalshop.com`
   679→**Auth:** `x-tts-access-token: <access_token>` header
   680→
   681→### Key Endpoints Used
   682→
   683→| Method | Path | Description |
   684→|--------|------|-------------|
   685→| GET | `/seller/202309/shops` | List shops |
   686→| GET | `/product/202309/products` | List products |
   687→| GET | `/product/202309/products/{id}` | Product detail |
   688→| PUT | `/product/202309/products/{id}` | Update product |
   689→| PUT | `/product/202309/inventories` | Update stock |
   690→| PUT | `/product/202309/products/{id}/prices` | Update price |
   691→| POST | `/product/202309/images/upload` | Upload image |
   692→| POST | `/api/v2/token/oauth/access_token` | Get access token |
   693→| POST | `/api/v2/token/refresh_token` | Refresh access token |
   694→
   695→**TikTok Update Inventory Request:**
   696→```typescript
   697→PUT /product/202309/inventories
   698→{
   699→  skus: Array<{
   700→    id: string;        // SKU/variant ID
   701→    inventory: Array<{
   702→      warehouse_id: string;
   703→      quantity: number;
   704→    }>;
   705→  }>;
   706→}
   707→```
   708→
   709→**TikTok Update Price Request:**
   710→```typescript
   711→PUT /product/202309/products/{product_id}/prices
   712→{
   713→  skus: Array<{
   714→    id: string;
   715→    sales_attributes: Array<{}>;
   716→    price: {
   717→      amount: string;        // string representation of price
   718→      currency: string;      // "IDR"
   719→    };
   720→  }>;
   721→}
   722→```
   723→
   724→**QPS Limit:** 20 requests/second for most endpoints.
   725→
   726→---
